RainbruRPG::Core::tCategoryTab

RainbruRPG::Core::tCategoryTab Struct Reference

#include <gscreateperso.h>

List of all members.

Detailed Description

A struct defining a category tab.

If own is true, the Tab pointer is used, otherwise, the ownerTab name is used.

The nextY value is used for the Irrlicht widget placement.
